{
  "id": "RAW_88de9324",
  "title": "最新 Agent 时代的“记忆系统”总览性综述英中对照版.pdf",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODkzMzMwMQ==&mid=2650450592&idx=1&sn=810434f28e1da98eb394bd9b7da4aefb",
  "date": "2025-12-31 08:26:00",
  "author": "AINLP",
  "siteName": "AINLP",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"0\" style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:20px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:12px;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">一、核心动机与贡献</span></span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"0\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是一篇<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">面向 2025 年后 AI Agent 时代的“记忆系统”总览性综述</span>，其核心判断是：</span></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:15px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n   <p data-start=\"202\" data-end=\"270\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><strong data-start=\"202\" data-end=\"270\"><span leaf=\"\">Memory（记忆）已经从一个“工程技巧”上升为 Agent 级智能的第一性原语（first-class primitive）。</span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"2\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者认为现有研究存在三大问题：</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"3\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">概念混乱</span>：Agent Memory、LLM Memory、RAG、Context Engineering 被大量混用</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"4\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">分类过时</span>：传统的“短期 / 长期记忆”已无法描述现代系统</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"5\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">研究碎片化</span>：方法、假设、评估体系彼此割裂</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"6\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">因此本文提出一个<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">统一的三维分析框架</span>，并系统梳理了<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">100+ 项代表性工作、基准与系统</span>memory-in-the-age-of-ai-agents。</span></p>\n  <h1 data-layout-id=\"8\" style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:20px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:12px;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">二、统一理论框架：Forms – Functions – Dynamics</span></span></h1>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"9\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">论文的最大贡献是提出了一个<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">三轴统一视角</span>，用于理解 Agent Memory：</span></p>\n  <h2 data-layout-id=\"11\" style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">1️⃣ Forms：记忆“长什么样”（载体形态）</span></h2>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"12\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者将 Agent Memory 按<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">存储位置与表示方式</span>分为三类：</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"14\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">外显、可编辑、可检索</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"15\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">以文本、图像、向量、结构化单元存在</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"16\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">是当前 Agent 系统中最常见的实现方式</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"17\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">进一步按<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">拓扑结构复杂度</span>细分为：</span></p>\n  <table>\n   <thead>\n    <tr>\n     <th>\n      <p style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">类型</span></p>\n     </th>\n     <th>\n      <p style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">特点</span></p>\n     </th>\n     <th>\n      <p style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">典型用途</span></p>\n     </th>\n    </tr>\n   </thead>\n   <tbody>\n    <tr>\n     <td>\n      <p style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Flat / 1D</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td>\n      <p style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">无结构，线性堆叠</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td>\n      <p style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">对话历史、chunk、经验池</span></p>\n     </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n     <td>\n      <p style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Planar / 2D</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td>\n      <p style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">单层结构（图/树）</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td>\n      <p style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">因果关系、任务依赖</span></p>\n     </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n     <td>\n      <p style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Hierarchical / 3D</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td>\n      <p style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">多层抽象结构</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td>\n      <p style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">长期知识 + 短期上下文</span></p>\n     </td>\n    </tr>\n   </tbody>\n  </table>\n  <blockquote style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:15px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n   <p data-start=\"959\" data-end=\"1050\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><strong data-start=\"959\" data-end=\"967\"><span leaf=\"\">关键洞见</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n     <br> \n    </span><span leaf=\"\">Flat Memory 强在覆盖与扩展；</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n     <br> \n    </span><span leaf=\"\">Graph / Hierarchical Memory 才是真正支持</span><strong data-start=\"1032\" data-end=\"1046\"><span leaf=\"\">推理、规划、抽象迁移</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">的关键。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <p data-layout-id=\"22\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">记忆<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">内化在模型参数中</span></span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"23\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">通过训练、微调、RL 写入</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"24\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">访问是隐式的、不可控的</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"25\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">优点：高效、无需检索</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"26\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">缺点：难以修改、不可解释、难以持续学习</span></p>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <p data-layout-id=\"29\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">位于模型的<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">隐状态 / 中间表示</span></span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"30\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">介于 token-level 与 parametric 之间</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"31\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">常用于长上下文、状态持续、隐式工作记忆</span></p>\n  <h2 data-layout-id=\"33\" style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">2️⃣ Functions：记忆“用来干什么”（功能角色）</span></h2>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"34\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">论文明确反对“短期 / 长期”这种时间维度分类，提出<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">功能性分类</span>：</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"36\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">世界知识、用户信息、角色设定</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"37\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">“我知道什么”</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"39\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">行为轨迹、成功/失败案例、策略抽象</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"40\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">“我做过什么、学到了什么”</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"41\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">👉 这是 Agent<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">持续改进、迁移学习、工具熟练度提升</span>的核心</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"43\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">当前任务中的中间状态、计划、草稿</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"44\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本质上是<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">受限上下文下的动态状态管理</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:15px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n   <p data-start=\"1589\" data-end=\"1657\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><strong data-start=\"1589\" data-end=\"1597\"><span leaf=\"\">重要判断</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n     <br> \n    </span><span leaf=\"\">真正区分“Agent”与“工具调用”的，不是 RAG，而是&nbsp;</span><strong data-start=\"1633\" data-end=\"1656\"><span leaf=\"\">Experiential Memory</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <h2 data-layout-id=\"47\" style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">3️⃣ Dynamics：记忆“如何形成与演化”（生命周期）</span></h2>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"48\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者用一个非常 Agent 化的视角，定义了记忆的三大操作算子：</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"50\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从原始交互中<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">抽取有价值信息</span></span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"51\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">不是“全存”，而是<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">选择性蒸馏</span></span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"53\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">合并、去重、冲突消解、抽象</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"54\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">引入<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">遗忘机制、RL 优化、结构重组</span></span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"56\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">与任务、状态、目标强相关</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"57\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">决定 Agent 是否“像在思考”</span></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:15px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n   <p data-start=\"1919\" data-end=\"1964\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">关键观点：</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n     <br> \n    </span><strong data-start=\"1929\" data-end=\"1964\"><span leaf=\"\">短期 / 长期不是结构，而是“调用频率 + 更新节奏”的结果。</span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <h1 data-layout-id=\"60\" style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:20px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:12px;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">三、与相关概念的系统区分（非常重要）</span></span></h1>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"61\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">论文专门用一整节澄清概念边界：</span></p>\n  <h2 data-layout-id=\"62\" style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Agent Memory vs LLM Memory</span></h2>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"63\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">LLM Memory</span>：模型内部 KV、长上下文、架构改进</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"64\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Agent Memory</span>：外显、可进化、跨任务</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"65\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">➡️ 前者是“模型能力”，后者是“智能体能力”</span></p>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <h2 data-layout-id=\"67\" style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Agent Memory vs RAG</span></h2>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"68\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">RAG：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">静态知识访问</span></span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"69\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Agent Memory：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">自我经验积累 + 持续演化</span></span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"70\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Agentic RAG 是交集，但<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">是否跨任务自我成长</span>是本质分界线。</span></p>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <h2 data-layout-id=\"72\" style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Agent Memory vs Context Engineering</span></h2>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"73\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Context Engineering：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">资源调度问题</span></span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"74\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Agent Memory：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">认知连续性问题</span></span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"75\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个解决“怎么塞进上下文”，</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"76\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个解决“我是谁、我学到了什么”。</span></p>\n  <h1 data-layout-id=\"78\" style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:20px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:12px;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">四、工程与研究资源价值</span></span></h1>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"79\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">论文系统整理了：</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"80\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">大量基准</span>：LoCoMo、LongMemEval、GAIA、SWE-bench、StreamBench 等</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"81\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">开源框架</span>：Mem0、Zep、A-MEM、G-Memory、HippoRAG 等</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"82\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">RL + Memory 方向</span>：Memory-R1、Mem-α、RMM</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"83\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">对做<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Agent 平台 / 长期助手 / 企业智能体</span>非常有参考价值 memory-in-the-age-of-ai-agents。</span></p>\n  <h1 data-layout-id=\"85\" style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:20px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:12px;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">五、未来研究前沿</span></span></h1>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"86\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者明确指出 5 个尚未成熟但<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">极具潜力</span>的方向：</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"87\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">自动化 Memory 设计</span>（让 Agent 学会“如何记忆”）</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"88\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Memory × Reinforcement Learning 深度融合</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"89\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">多模态记忆（视频 / 空间 / 具身）</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"90\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">多 Agent 共享记忆</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"91\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">可信与安全问题</span>（隐私、污染、记忆投毒）</span></p>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <p data-start=\"1979\" data-end=\"2076\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:24px;\"><strong data-start=\"1979\" data-end=\"2074\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">附该综述英中对照版，总共 2